  "name": "echidnabot",
  "description": "Proof-aware CI bot that orchestrates the ECHIDNA theorem-proving platform for automatic formal-proof verification on every push and pull request. Bridges GitHub, GitLab, and Bitbucket webhooks to ECHIDNA's multi-prover backend (Coq, Lean 4, Agda, Isabelle/HOL, Z3, CVC5, Metamath, HOL Light, Mizar, PVS, ACL2, HOL4) with container isolation, retry / circuit-breaker, a 5-level trust bridge, and a four-mode response policy.",
  "version": "0.1.0",
